pan class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 30, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jqk1665703133137.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jqk1665703133137.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jqk1665703133137.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jqk1665703133137\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"jqk1665703133137__ugetreg_403724\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Get the integer value of a Uniface general variable ($1 ... $99).</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"jqk1665703133137__topic_d120479e1_d120480e1_d120481e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"jqk1665703133137__codeblock_tql_dm1_1wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">long ugetreg (shortnum);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jqk1665703133137__topic_d85672e1_d85673e1_d85674e1_d85675e1_d85676e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d673204e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"jqk1665703133137__d6450e20\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">num</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Number of the Uniface general variable. Allowed values are 1 through 99.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jqk1665703133137__topic_d85677e1_d85678e1_d85679e1_d85680e1_d85681e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d673204e80\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jqk1665703133137__p_d120494e1_d120495e1_d120496e1\">The integer value of the specified general\n            variable. If the value of <var class=\"keyword varname\">num</var> is out of range, this function returns\n            1. However, nnote that this is also the return value when <var class=\"keyword varname\">num</var> is\n            within the range and the general variable has the value 1.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jqk1665703133137__topic_d85682e1_d85683e1_d85684e1_d85685e1_d85686e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d673204e95\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jqk1665703133137__d5947e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jqk1665703133137__topic_d85687e1_d85688e1_d85689e1_d85690e1_d85691e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d673204e108\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jqk1665703133137__p_d120506e1_d120507e1_d120508e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ugetreg</code> returns the integer value\n            of the specified Uniface general variable (historically also known as a ‘dollar\n            register’), or 1 (one) if the specified register does not exist. If the general variable\n            does not contain a numeric value, the return value is zero. If the general variable\n            contains a non-integer numeric value, the fractional part is dropped and only the\n            integer part is returned.</p>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following code fragment retrieves the integer value of the contents of the general variable <code class=\"ph codeph\">$10</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104jqk1665703133137_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"jqk1665703133137__codeblock_djc_qm1_1wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\nint value = ugetreg(10);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyf1665703133267.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ugetregf</a><p>Get the double-precision value of a Uniface general variable ($1 ... $99).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wvm1665703133337.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ugetregs</a><p>Get the string value of a Uniface general variable ($1 ... $99).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wrj1665703133411.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uputreg</a><p>Copy a long integer value into the specified general variable ($1 ... $99).</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528999\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528999\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ugetreg Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 30, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Get the integer value of a Uniface general variable ($1 ... $99). long ugetreg (shortnum); Copy Parameters num Number of the Uniface general variable. Allowed values are 1 through 99. Return Values The integer value of the specified general variable. If the value of num is out of range, this function returns 1. However, nnote that this is also the return value when num is within the range and the general variable has the value 1. Use Library: yrtl Description ugetreg returns the integer value of the specified Uniface general variable (historically also known as a ‘dollar register’), or 1 (one) if the specified register does not exist. If the general variable does not contain a numeric value, the return value is zero. If the general variable contains a non-integer numeric value, the fractional part is dropped and only the integer part is returned. The following code fragment retrieves the integer value of the contents of the general variable $10 : Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> int value = ugetreg(10); Copy Related Links ugetregf Get the double-precision value of a Uniface general variable ($1 ... $99). ugetregs Get the string value of a Uniface general variable ($1 ... $99). uputreg Copy a long integer value into the specified general variable ($1 ... $99). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}